[{"url_token": "leng-mian-xia-65", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "10333824028", "reply_comment_id": "0", "reply_root_comment_id": "10333824028", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>全球版是什么意思？</p>", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "冷面侠", "author_id": "1bbd55dd3ec515b66cc7ca7d73a24996", "author_is_anonymous": false, "child_comment": [{"url_token": "comiceix", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "10334058920", "reply_comment_id": "10332965239", "reply_root_comment_id": "10333824028", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "是这样。如果完全不了解的话还是不建议拿自己的主力机尝试，先备用机慢慢了解一下比较好。", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "ComiceIX", "author_id": "3d3dd29c9d6a999c8af3e9e812d0f605", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "comiceix", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "10333882989", "reply_comment_id": "10333824028", "reply_root_comment_id": "10333824028", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "就是海外（虽然不一定是所有国家，比如国产厂商进不去美国）销售的同款机型的名字，比如Note11TPro只有中国版叫这个名字，海外版叫PocoX4GT，印度版叫K50i，实际上这些都是同一款手机。", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "ComiceIX", "author_id": "3d3dd29c9d6a999c8af3e9e812d0f605", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "leng-mian-xia-65", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "10333617785", "reply_comment_id": "10333882989", "reply_root_comment_id": "10333824028", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>嗷，那全球版的话，用国外的谷歌商店，是通过刷机吗？</p>", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "冷面侠", "author_id": "1bbd55dd3ec515b66cc7ca7d73a24996", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "comiceix", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "10333354031", "reply_comment_id": "10333617785", "reply_root_comment_id": "10333824028", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "是的，因为硬件完全一致，可以完美刷海外版的官方系统包，不会担心刷翻车。除了谷歌全家桶以外，海外版系统的精简度和广告方面也稍微好点。", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "ComiceIX", "author_id": "3d3dd29c9d6a999c8af3e9e812d0f605", "author_is_anonymous": false}, {"url_token": "leng-mian-xia-65", "headline": "", "is_advertiser": false, "comment_id": "10332965239", "reply_comment_id": "10333354031", "reply_root_comment_id": "10333824028", "hot": false, "is_author": false, "is_author_top": false, "content": "<p>刷机这个我完全不懂。不过我听说现在好多手机刷机前都要申请什么锁，并且管理得很严格。你的意思是解锁后自己刷机吗？</p>", "like_count": 0, "author_name": "冷面侠", "author_id": "1bbd55dd3ec515b66cc7ca7d73a24996", "author_is_anonymous": false}]}]